        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4263",
        "content": "\"Come in, mr Lawley,\" said Thorndyke, rather stiffly, and, as he held the door open, the two visitors entered.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
