        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4263",
        "content": "\"I say-do you want me to go?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4263_16194_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4263/16194/4263_16194_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4263",
        "content": "\"No, I don't.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4263_16194_000028_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4263/16194/4263_16194_000028_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4263",
        "content": "He seized her wrists and turned her away from the table and continued to look into her eyes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4263_16194_000028_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4263/16194/4263_16194_000028_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4263",
        "content": "She twisted about, looking away from him, but the burning blush made even the little ear she turned toward him pink, and he loved it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
