        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4263",
        "content": "\"Most eighteen, I know, because-\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4263_16194_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4263/16194/4263_16194_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4263",
        "content": "\"Well, anyway, mother says no girl of hers shall marry before she's of age, and she says that means twenty one, and-\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
